Search for symbol definitions

Usage: kodex search [OPTIONS] [QUERY]

Arguments:
  [QUERY]  Symbol name, FQN, or FQN suffix to search for (optional when --module is provided)

Options:
      --idx <IDX>          Path to kodex.idx (default: .scalex/kodex.idx, or `KODEX_IDX` env var)
      --kind <KIND>        Filter by symbol kind [possible values: class, case-class, trait, object, method, field, type, constructor, enum]
      --module <MODULE>    Filter by module name (substring match; dotted patterns match segments in order)
      --limit <LIMIT>      [default: 50]
      --exclude <EXCLUDE>  
      --include-noise      Include noise (generated code, plumbing methods, etc.) — excluded by default
  -h, --help               Print help

